subtitle: Join GTA+ for Benefits
content:
Join GTA Online’s premium Membership program, delivering exclusive benefits and rewards to GTA+ Members each month, including GTA$500,000 and more. GTA+ Members can claim the below through January 7:

— The new Vapid FMJ MK V (Super)
— A GTA$1,000,000 discount on new Prix Luxury Mansion properties
— Early Access to the Progen Luiva (Super)
— The Santa Skull Sweater and Santa Skull Track Pants
— And more
